result.name: Aidan Korean Dessert Cafe

reviews.text: We had 14 people for lunch today. The waiter was helpful, arranged us a long table right away. The food taste was not bad and price was economy for all set lunch.
Very affordable dinner set for two people! It has a wide range of food selection and it was very delicious!

Basically everything was good. Long queue during dinner time on a weekday so I would recommend to reserve a table first.

The cheesy dish is so satisfying that it is a must order if you love cheese. The stone pot one is okay, with enough portion and ingredients. Slightly slightly overpriced I would say. If there's no 10% service charge, I will for sure come again.

By the way, the service was really so so, maybe because of the high amount of diners.

This place is a little bit hidden away, not the easiest place to find.
The prices are quite reasonable, especially when considering the average prices for Korean food in Hong Kong! 
The food is good and so are their desserts. 
The only thing one should be aware of before dining there is that some times they will take an extremely long time to serve you. I have dined there three times with a group where one or two from the group had to wait till after the rest of us finished eating, before their food was served.
Nice food, big portions.

result.name: 小火焰韓式咖啡餐廳

reviews.text: 味道同服務都超一流👍可惜未有招牌菜試到

夜晚都幾多人排隊，7點左右餐廳就full。我地都覺得食物好一般，味道普通，份量又少。
雨衣甘藍特色菜餅（$48）-份量少，雨衣甘藍得4-5片，味道好一般
脆米豬手沙律 （$88）-唔建議叫，啲豬手勁'嚡' ，味道唔太好，菜又唔多，食唔到有脆米
拉絲芝士bb豬肋骨拌泡菜炒飯（$88）-我想知點解啲人推介呢個？我地個飯完全拉唔到絲，啲芝士係類似白汁嘅醬，無芝士味，啲飯又勁少，每人得兩/三啖。個豬肋骨有好多bbq醬之餘又乾乾地。好伏...
唔知點解仲會有咁多人？
同埋2人枱同旁邊啲人太close，連條gap都無，唔方便傾計。
試左個溫泉蛋會牛肋拌飯同埋叫咗個醬燒豬頸肉番茄湯烏冬兩個加埋都係$110仲要唔使+1個牛肋條配飯好惹味 配埋啲紫菜鹹香味冇得頂個烏冬係手打烏冬所以配埋個番茄湯都係冇得輸
以地鐵站不算太就腳，食物水準ok，午餐價錢公道。
We had 14 people for lunch today. The waiter was helpful, arranged us a long table right away. The food taste was not bad and price was economy for all set lunch.
